"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Masuki...? Hey, now's probably not the best time...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event237-06-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"... What?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf_right01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Uh~... I don't really know either. I just kinda came.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Huh? Sheesh. You sometimes act with incredibly little forethought, don't you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"If I wanted your opinion, I'd have asked for it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"serious03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf_left01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf_right01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Hey... I know what you said earlier, but I actually kinda think we're on track to \"change the world.\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Huh? On what basis?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"I dunno if it counts as a basis, but...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"... Take a look at this. You've been so busy you haven't been checkin' any social media, have you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Yeah, I haven't. So?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"These are the posts by some fans who grabbed some of our flyers at Galaxy.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"\"Can't wait for RAS's solo concert...\" \"I handed out lots of flyers at school...\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"And I'm guessin' these ones are by the people who became our fans as a result of the contests we've been in.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"... \"I've been curious about RAS, so I grabbed a ticket.\" \"Was torn between Midnight-Peaky and RAS, but I picked RAS.\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"There's still more. See? I mean, sure, just about everyone's talkin' about Midnight-Peaky, but there are still plenty of folks who are talkin' about us.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"This counts as pretty good proof that we're on track to change the world, don't you think?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"I mean, just look at all these people who are sayin' they like our music.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"It's also a whole lot more than when we started out, wouldn't you say?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"... I've always believed in your whole \"Change the world\" thing, you know?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"What...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Although the first time you said it, it did come across as a childishly naive dream. After all, bein' a backup drummer, I'd seen how harsh the music industry could be.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"But once I joined RAS and we finished puttin' the crew together... I seriously started believin' that with all of us together, we could change the world.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"That's what made me decide to stick with you. Doesn't matter where we go, even to hell. I've made up my mind to play the drums here till I die.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"You're the one who made me feel this way, so stop tryin' to throw in the towel!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"I-I'm not...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Then stop lookin' at the ground!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"There ain't no way for someone who always looks down to change the world!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"The only place you should be lookin' is straight ahead with your head high and that bratty smirk on your face.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-063","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Isn't that the kinda person our producer is supposed to be, CHU²?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-064","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"... You sure have some nerve telling me what to do... Who gave you the right anyway...?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-065","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Argh~... I've had just about enough!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-066","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Ow!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-067","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"That was some big talk.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-068","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Let's see if you can back it up. I'm going to work you to the bone until... no, even after we change the world.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-069","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"You asked for it, MASKING!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-070","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Too easy. Bring it on.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-071","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-072","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"PAREO, ticket!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-073","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"Y-yes! I assume you mean a ticket for our concert?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event237-06-074","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Of course! And get me an envelope while you're at it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-075","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"What are you going to do, CHU²?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event237-06-076","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Issue a challenge. I'm inviting Ms. Hayamiya to our concert.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-077","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"A-are you sure that's a good idea?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event237-06-078","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"She did throw the first punch. Yo, CHU², if you're doin' it, you might as well give her a seat where she can see us real good.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"kime01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event237-06-079","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"I fully intend to. Fortunately, there are plenty of seats to choose from. Somewhere in the middle a little ways back should give her the best view of the stage.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event237-06-080","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"I see... Looks like we're going to have to make sure our performance is good enough to give her a proper \"welcome.\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"kime01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event237-06-081"